{"tid":941900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寶生莉莉上月否認有HIV 今個月忽然引退","createTime":"2018-12-15T07:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T10:45:56.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"68b6af38fb5939afb5d6e453aefad675a3b510cc","tid":941900,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"日本AV界近期出現引退潮，不少著名女優已先後宣佈「收山」，計有吉澤明步、水原乃亞、佐佐木明希等等，而另一女神寶生莉莉日前都已在Twitter宣佈引退，佢留言話：「從今天開始，我不再屬於AV界...」寶生莉莉嘅即日退役宣言引起關注，事關佢不止一次有神化舉動，佢在直播時吞下大量藥物嘅情景令人記憶猶新，舉止十分詭異。<br />\n<br />\n寶生莉莉冇拍愛情動作片已有一段時間，早前AV界驚爆有女優感染HIV，寶生莉莉即時跳出來搶答，唔止公開HIV測試後呈陰性嘅結果，又自爆今年8月底開始已冇再拍片，舉動之大令人摸不着頭腦，如今引退自然引來更多揣測。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181214/large/1544783558_ca6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181214%2Flarge%2F1544783558_ca6a.jpg&h=ac29f40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181214/large/1544783524_26fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181214%2Flarge%2F1544783524_26fd.jpg&h=8b1437f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 揾港男埋單啦"},{"pid":"19eb6c5c39f6820f33bf21b55efb34041924d2ef","tid":941900,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"呢排好多人走"},{"pid":"b468c9924768f2b1c22c21dded685aa2d1b863ac","tid":941900,"uid":25062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"唔想做都要比理由？我日日都想辭職啦"},{"pid":"0d55fe80bcb262d117590b88dc6478420d364b32","tid":941900,"uid":111872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:07:48.000Z","msg":"其實佢係咪假波"},{"pid":"c23fc3f66c4d1c330f01df2e53fe734b85513e91","tid":941900,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d55fe80bcb262d117590b88dc6478420d364b32","tid":941900,"u